I am happy to receive contributions to this repository, so long as you agree
to release your work under the 3 clause version of the BSD license. If you
make non-trivial changes to an existing file, then feel free to add your name
with mine in the copyright notice (with the correct year). Simply add
the 3 clause version of the BSD license with your name (and the year) to new
files that you make. You can contact me if you want to gain direct access to
the repository.

Enjoy,
Logan =)_
